# Local development can query Cloudflare D1/R2 through REST when native Worker bindings
# are not available in Vite dev. Put real values in .env.local only.
#
# Required in .env.local for local D1/R2 REST fallback:
# CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID
# CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN or CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ACCESS_TOKEN
#
# Optional local overrides:
# QUESTION_DB_DATABASE_ID
# PERSONAL_DB_DATABASE_ID
# QUESTION_R2_BUCKET_NAME
#
# Optional local dev auth override. When DEV_AUTH_USER_ID is set, local Vite dev
# treats every request as this signed-in user without Google OAuth.
# DEV_AUTH_USER_ID
# DEV_AUTH_EMAIL
# DEV_AUTH_NAME
# DEV_AUTH_PHOTO_URL
#
# Required for Vercel Codex proxy-backed ChatGPT grading:
# CHATGPT_CODEX_PROXY_URL
# CHATGPT_CODEX_PROXY_API_KEY
# CHATGPT_RESPONSES_WEBSOCKET_MODE
